Lyrics

Dixita

Bheta hamro ajkal sadhai huncha
Kura timro ra mero maya nai parey jasto suncha
Asti asti samma maya ma fasne kama
Ta ma gardai gardina bhandai thiyeu ta
 
Jasari huncha timi malai aile bhetna au
Jasari huncha timi malai nai bhetna au
Au au au aile bhetna au
Au au aile
 
Ajkal ma japi basirachu timro nama
Naherana timi malai tesari
Fasai malai chodi jane ho ki

Hijo rati sapani ma
Timilai ma khojira thye
Hunu parne cheu mai timi
Hunchau kaha yaha bahek
Chaidaina malai kei pani
Rakhechu timilai mana ma
Satya cha yo kura
Satya cha yo kura

Lil Buddha aka Young Lion

Young lion
 
Malai pani fasna man thyena
Tara aba dubna gahirai baki rahena
Jana dinna timro maya khera
Agi badchu aba timilai sangai lera
Tesaile bhana timro man ma k cha
Yo man le thamna sakena
Hami dui bich ko duri
Tesaile aaideu ma nera
Aaja nai aauchu timro ghara
Malai pani lagcha testai dara tara
Dekhchu ma sapana hamro ghar baseko
Tin char ota nani timro mero
Mero bhawana timi bujha
Timi afno man ko kura suna
Kaile pani dinna timilai dukha
Timi ra ma sadhai sadhai lai
Dukha nadium hamro mana lai

Dixita

Jasari huncha timi malai aile bhetna au
Jasari huncha timi malai nai bhetna au
Au au au aile bhetna au
Au au aile

YB Records

snippet.title: DEEWANIYAT Title Track - Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat | Harshvardhan Sonam | Vishal ,KaushikGuddu,Kunaal
snippet.description:
EXPERIENCE THE MADNESS OF LOVE, WHERE PASSION TURNS INTO “DEEWANIYAT”.

THE MOST AWAITED TITLE TRACK “DEEWANIYAT” FROM “EK DEEWANE KI DEEWANIYAT” IS HERE!

ANSHUL GARG presents 
A DESI MOVIES FACTORY PRODUCTION

“EK DEEWANE KI DEEWANIYAT”

DIRECTED BY: Milap Milan Zaveri
PRODUCED BY: Anshul Garg, Dinesh Jain
CO-PRODUCER: Raghav Sharma

RELEASING Worldwide this DIWALI on 21st OCTOBER, 2025 IN CINEMAS near you.

Streaming Link 👉🏼 https://VirginMusicGroup.lnk.to/Deewaniyat

Director of Photography: Nigam Bomzan
Editor: Maahir Zaveri
Background Score: John Stewart Eduri
Sound Design: Kunal Mehta, Parikshit Lalvani
Production Designers: Tajamul Shaikh, Anshita Manot
Costume Designer: Avani Pratap Gumber
Choreography: Adil Shaikh
Action Director: Ajay Thakur Pathania
Creative Director: Adil Shaikh
Associate Editor: Sachin Kunal
Head of Production: Gaurav Arora
Post Producer: Abhineet Singh Rajput
Associate Director: Ankit Choudhary
Executive Producer: Rahul Sehal
Casting Director: Paragg Mehta
Line Producer: RS Films, Abdul Vahid M
Production Controller: Manmohan Devsar Ladi

Music: Kaushik-Guddu
Lyrics: Kunaal Vermaa
Singers: Vishal Mishra
Mix and mastered by Shadab Rayeen @ New Edge 
Assistant engineers - Jazbaat, Sohamm, Prasad.
Music Producer : ZIA and Kaushik-Guddu
Acoustic and electric guitars designed and performed : Prachotosh Appai Bhowmick
Bass guitar designed and performed : Raj Kumar Dewan 
Bouzuki and Mandolin : Tapas Roy
Dholak and Tabla : Ratnadeep Jamsandekar & Sandesh Kadam
Harmonium : Omkar Agnihotri 
Chorus : Kaushik-Guddu and Samyak Prasanna 
Recorded @studio 504 : Rahul M Sharma

DI & Sound: Futureworks Media Ltd
Colorist: Tushar Desai
Re-recording: Debajit Changmai

Visual Promotions: MA+TH (Marching Ants + Trigger Happy), Member of Hakuhodo International
Publicity Design: Parass Kanani (House of Awe)
Publicity Stills: Avinash Gowarikar

Digital Marketing Partners: EveryMedia Technologies, DotGrip, HiFi Digital

Play DMF Team :-
Founder & CEO: Anshul Garg
Vice President: Raghav Sharma (Pratick Sharma)
Label Manager: Sankalp Garg
Project Head: Gaurav Arora
Legal & Digital Manager: Ashima Chauhan
Team: Aansi & Anshu Prasad
Artwork: Vicky Sandhu
Special Thanks: Virgin Music India

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria


Lyrics :- 
Tere dil pe haq mera hai
Tu sanam beshaq mera
Phir lakeerein hon ya na ho
Tu mera hai tu mera hai

Jo tu aag hai
Haan to phir mujhe
Jalne ka shauk hai
Jalne ka shauk hai
Marne se kahin
Jyada haan tujhe
Khone ka khauf hai
Khone ka khauf hai

Tu chahiye mujhe
Chahe kahe ise 
Mera junoon ya phir 
Tu zid meri


Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe likh chuka hoon
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi ki
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai 
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera


Paane ki tujhko
Hasrat liye hi
Raaton ko main
Jagta hoon
Kyu jaane phir bhi
Dushaman teri do
Ankhon ko 
Main lagta hoon
Kahe na chahe tu mujhe
Karunga tujhe ishq main
Mujhe ye parwaah nahi 
Jo bhi ho mera anjaam har haal mein
Tu chahiye mujhe
Jo bhi saza mile 
Parwaah hai phir kise
Anjaam ki 
Tu hi armaan tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi deewaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe 
Likh chuka hu
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera

#harshvardhanrane #sonambajwa #EkDeewaneKiDeewaniyat #MilapMilanZaveri #DeewaniyatKiDiwali #DesiMoviesFactory #playdmf #vishalmishra #tumerahai #fida #teredilpehaqmerahai

snippet.title: JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 | Official Teaser | Crunchyroll
snippet.description:
JUJUTSU KAISEN Season 3 is coming exclusively to Crunchyroll January 2026! Watch JUJUTSU KAISEN Crunchyroll! https://got.cr/cc-jjkpv

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. Guided by the most powerful of sorcerers, Satoru Gojo, Itadori is admitted to Tokyo Jujutsu High School, an organization that fights the curses... and thus begins the heroic tale of a boy who became a curse to exorcise a curse, a life from which he could never turn back.

Crunchyroll brings you the latest clips, openings, full episodes, and more from your favorite anime!

snippet.title: Baahubali: The Epic - Official Trailer (2025)
snippet.description:
Before RRR took the world by storm, master filmmaker S.S. Rajamouli redefined Indian Cinema with his two-part BAAHUBALI saga. Now, the epic tale of royalty, revenge, kings, and wars has been personally re-edited by the master himself from two films into a single unforgettable cinematic experience, with fully remastered picture and sound (and a few new surprises), so audiences can reunite to experience the euphoria the way it was intended: on the big screen, together. 

When a lost prince is rescued and raised in exile, he grows up unaware of his past. Years later, he returns to uncover the truth about his father’s murder and his mother’s imprisonment, and must rise to reclaim his place as the rightful king.

Baahubali: The Epic will be released in theaters across the U.S. October 31st.

#IGN #Movies

( तिम्रोलागि आउला, तिमिलाई लगुम्ला)

मेरा इजा भन्नान मेरा बा भन्नान, मेरा इजा भन्नान बा भन्नान ब्वारि चाईयो चेला  
 ( मेरो आमा बुवा भन्नु हुन्छन उहालाई बुहारि चाईयो रे)

कति लागे पुछड तेरा आज पडी फेला अ  हँ...!!!
 ( कति तिम्रो पछि लागे, बल्ल आज भेटियौ )

तेरी मम्मि कसम ! बरेति ल्यौलो तेरा घर आइरैछि मन 
 ( तिम्रो मम्मि कसम ,  तिमि यति मन पर्या छौ कि तिम्रो घर जन्ति लियेर आउनेछु )

बनारस कि साडी तुलाई टनकपुर कि लेहंगा 
 ( तिम्रो लागि बनारसको साडि अनि टनकपुरको लेहेङगा ल्याईदिम्ला )

उल्या मुल्या जन सोचें चेला हम पहाडका
 ( हामिलाई बेताले मान्छे नसोच्नु हामि पहाडका छोरा हौ )

 ओ सासु ! तमकी गोला मिसिरि कन्यादान गरी दिया गर्लो चाकरी 
  ( वो मेरि सासुआमा तपाईको लागि मैले नरिवल मिसृ (सगुन) ल्याईदेको छु तपाई को छोरिको सेवा गर्नेछु कन्यादान गरि मलाई दिनु )

अँ…. घोडा चडि औँलो मुई जग्गेमा रिटौलो मुई रातो ले सजौलो मुई तुलाई आफ्नो बनौलो मुई 
 ( म दुलाहा बनेर घोडा चडेर आउला अनि मण्डपमा फेरा गरेर तिमिलाई सिन्दुर हालि रातोले सजाउला, अनि तिमिलाई आफ्नो बनाउला )

अँ.…आफ्नो भुण्णे कत्ती छन् मुई त तेरो हु सुण्णि कन !
 ( म आफ्नो हु भन्ने धेरै हुन्छन तर म तिम्रै हु तिमि मेरो कुरा  सुन )

पुतली पुतली ए पुतली ए पुतली इथ आई पुतली 
 (पुतली पुतली ए पुतली !)
 
पुतली पुतली ए पुतली ए पुतली इथ आई पुतली 
  ( ए पुतली यता आउ पुतली )

हँम...... बझाङगी चेली मू तमी पड्या वैतडा,
 चुखचाटा हरामी हुँदा छाड तमी पुण झा !
 ( म बझाङ कि छोरि परे तपाई बैतडिका पर्नुभो ,  बैतडा चुख्चाटा हरामि हुन्छन तपाई म बाट टाडै बस्नु )

तेरा ईजा मानी ग्या तेरा बा मानी ग्या तु क्यान नामान्नी छै मुखी राई नी क्या !
 ( तिम्रो बुवा आमाले म सङग बिहेको लागि हुन्छ भनिसक्यो
 तिमिले मलाई आहिले सम्म चिनेऔ )
 
यो बैतडो हरामि हा ! हा !हा ! तुखि बनाउने हो स्वनी ओ ! हो !
 (यो बैतडो हरामि तिमिलाई आफ्नो स्वास्नि बनायेरै छोड्छु )

 मूखि भिना भनुन्ना  तेरा नक्कली भनुन्ना
 ( तिम्रो नक्कली बैनि मलाई भिनाजु भन्लान )

तु आउनी है क्या बझाङगी सेल खिलौने है क्या !
 ( तिमि आउछौ र ? मलाई बझाङ्गि सेल खुवाछौ र?

माया को जाल बिछौंनी है क्या !
कपटी तेरा जाल मी फसौनी है क्या !
( मलाई कपटेर आफ्नो माया जालमा फसाउने हौ र?  )
 
फसा तेरा  जाल मी फस्दिउलो झा 
 ( तिम्रो मायाजालामा मलाई फसाउ,  म फस्न तयार छु )

हामी दुई की जोडी धेकी मान्नाछन डाँ
 ( हामि दुईको जोडि देखेर मान्छे डाहा रिस मान्छन )

लाई देखा कोई  मेरी पुतली की आखो त उईका छाती मी होलो धा! धा! धा! ए पुतली ❤️
  ( मेरि पुतलिलाई कसैले आखा लगायो भने
 त्यस्को छाति भरि गोलि हान्दिन्छु )

 ( तिम्रो मम्मि कसम ,  तिमि यति मन पर्या छौ कि तिम्रो घर जन्ति लियेर आउनेछु )

बनारस कि साडी तुलाई टनकपुर कि लेहंगा 
 ( तिम्रो लागि बनारसको साडि अनि टनकपुरको लेहेङगा ल्याईदिम्ला )

उल्या मुल्या जन सोचें चेला हम पहाडका
 ( हामिलाई बेताले मान्छे नसोच्नु हामि पहाडका छोरा हौ )

 ओ सासु ! तमकी गोला मिसिरि कन्यादान गरी दिया गर्लो चाकरी 
  ( वो मेरि सासुआमा तपाईको लागि मैले नरिवल मिसृ (सगुन) ल्याईदेको छु तपाई को छोरिको सेवा गर्नेछु कन्यादान गरि मलाई दिनु )

अँ…. घोडा चडि औँलो मुई जग्गेमा रिटौलो मुई रातो ले सजौलो मुई तुलाई आफ्नो बनौलो मुई 
 ( म दुलाहा बनेर घोडा चडेर आउला अनि मण्डपमा फेरा गरेर तिमिलाई सिन्दुर हालि रातोले सजाउला, अनि तिमिलाई आफ्नो बनाउला )

अँ.…आफ्नो भुण्णे कत्ती छन् मुई त तेरो हु सुण्णि कन !
 ( म आफ्नो हु भन्ने धेरै हुन्छन तर म तिम्रै हु तिमि मेरो कुरा  सुन )

पुतली पुतली ए पुतली ए पुतली इथ आई पुतली 
 (पुतली पुतली ए पुतली !)
 
पुतली पुतली ए पुतली ए पुतली इथ आई पुतली 
  ( ए पुतली यता आउ पुतली )

हँम...... बझाङगी चेली मू तमी पड्या वैतडा,
 चुखचाटा हरामी हुँदा छाड तमी पुण झा !
 ( म बझाङ कि छोरि परे तपाई बैतडिका पर्नुभो ,  बैतडा चुख्चाटा हरामि हुन्छन तपाई म बाट टाडै बस्नु )

तेरा ईजा मानी ग्या तेरा बा मानी ग्या तु क्यान नामान्नी छै मुखी राई नी क्या !
 ( तिम्रो बुवा आमाले म सङग बिहेको लागि हुन्छ भनिसक्यो
 तिमिले मलाई आहिले सम्म चिनेऔ )
 
यो बैतडो हरामि हा ! हा !हा ! तुखि बनाउने हो स्वनी ओ ! हो !
 (यो बैतडो हरामि तिमिलाई आफ्नो स्वास्नि बनायेरै छोड्छु )

 मूखि भिना भनुन्ना  तेरा नक्कली भनुन्ना
 ( तिम्रो नक्कली बैनि मलाई भिनाजु भन्लान )

तु आउनी है क्या बझाङगी सेल खिलौने है क्या !
 ( तिमि आउछौ र ? मलाई बझाङ्गि सेल खुवाछौ र?

माया को जाल बिछौंनी है क्या !
कपटी तेरा जाल मी फसौनी है क्या !
( मलाई कपटेर आफ्नो माया जालमा फसाउने हौ र?  )
 
फसा तेरा  जाल मी फस्दिउलो झा 
 ( तिम्रो मायाजालामा मलाई फसाउ,  म फस्न तयार छु )

हामी दुई की जोडी धेकी मान्नाछन डाँ
 ( हामि दुईको जोडि देखेर मान्छे डाहा रिस मान्छन )

लाई देखा कोई  मेरी पुतली की आखो त उईका छाती मी होलो धा! धा! धा! ए पुतली ❤️
  ( मेरि पुतलिलाई कसैले आखा लगायो भने
 त्यस्को छाति भरि गोलि हान्दिन्छु )
  सुन्दर सुदूरपश्चिम नेपाल♥️🧿🚀

About YRF Spy Universe:
YRF Spy Universe is a first of its kind cinematic universe of spy thriller films in India. The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. "Pathaan" was the fourth instalment in the Spy Universe franchise which was released in 2023 starring Shah Rukh Khan, Deepika Padukone and John Abraham. "Tiger 3", the fifth instalment in the YRF Spy Universe and the third film in the Tiger series, starring Salman Khan, Katrina Kaif and Emraan Hashmi, released in 2023. "War 2", the sixth film in the YRF Spy Universe, starring Hrithik Roshan, NTR and Kiara Advani, directed by Ayan Mukerji, released on 14 August 2025. "Alpha", the seventh film in the franchise and Hindi cinema’s first female-led YRF Spy Universe film, starring Alia Bhatt and Sharvari, will release on 25 December 2025.

The first film in the universe, "Ek Tha Tiger", starring Salman Khan and Katrina Kaif was released in 2012, followed by its sequel "Tiger Zinda Hai" in 2017. The third film in the universe, "War" was released in 2019 and starred Hrithik Roshan and Tiger Shroff in pivotal roles. snippet.title: Dil Madharaasi - Official Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | Vidyut | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
The wait ends here with the official trailer of Dil Madharaasi, a high-octane action-drama starring Sivakarthikeyan, Rukmini Vasanth, and Vidyut Jammwal in pivotal roles. Directed by the visionary A.R. Murugadoss and backed by a powerful soundtrack from Anirudh Ravichander, the film promises a perfect blend of adrenaline-pumping action, deep emotional layers, and an intense story. Sivakarthikeyan steps into a never-before-seen role, showcasing raw intensity and charisma, while Vidyut Jammwal amps up the thrill with his trademark action sequences.

With grand visuals, gripping storytelling, and a soundtrack that elevates every moment, Dil Madharaasi is set to become a blockbuster Tamil movie of 2025. If you're searching for the latest Sivakarthikeyan movie, Anirudh Ravichander music, or a trailer that delivers both mass appeal and cinematic quality, this one hits all the marks. Don’t miss the most-awaited Tamil action drama trailer—Dil Madharaasi is here to steal the spotlight and set the screens on fire.

#DilMadharaasi Grand release worldwide on September 5th ❤‍🔥

snippet.description:
Even greater changes are still to come.

Watch the trailer for #28YearsLater: The Bone Temple - exclusively in movie theatres 1.16.26.

Follow Us on Social:

Subscribe for more exclusive content: https://www.youtube.com/@sonypictures

Expanding upon the world created by Danny Boyle and Alex Garland in 28 Years Later but turning that world on its head - Nia DaCosta directs 28 Years Later: The Bone Temple. In a continuation of the epic story, Dr. Kelson (Ralph Fiennes) finds himself in a shocking new relationship - with consequences that could change the world as they know it - and Spike's (Alfie Williams) encounter with Jimmy Crystal (Jack O'Connell) becomes a nightmare he can't escape. In the world of The Bone Temple, the infected are no longer the greatest threat to survival - the inhumanity of the survivors can be stranger and more terrifying.
 
Directed by:​​
Nia DaCosta​​​
​

📝 Lyrics

MUKHDA
Goliyan chal gayeen
Chhuriyan chal gayeen
Saare shaher ki
Kudiyan jal gayeen

Goliyan chal gayeen
Chhuriyan chal gayeen
Shaher ki
Kudiyan jal gayeen

Mausam ka haal bhi tere
Control mein hai janeman

Ke दिसम्बर mein bhi tujhse
Milke garmi lagti hai

[Laal colour ki saari mein 
Kudiye tu Danger lagti hai] ×2

Oomph tera dekhke
मुंडेयाँ di jaan सुलगदी hai

Laal colour ki saari mein 
Kudiye tu Danger lagti hai]



ANTARA
Jis color ke kapde tere
Vaisa tera mood hai
Blue mein kardi charming baatein
Black mein tu rude hai

Yash chopra ki lagdi
Chaandnii tu white mein
50 Shades wala tera
Grey mein attitude hai

Aur pink mein तो pankhudi
Lagti hai tu gulaab ki

Ek hi rang hai jisme
Baby tu ख़ंजर lagdi ae

Laal color ki saar mein
Kudiye tu Danger lagdi ae

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------

snippet.title: Bijuria | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari | Varun, Janhvi,Sanya, Rohit | Sonu, Tanishk, Ravi, Asees
snippet.description:
Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe giraye re bijuria, bijuria ⚡

A firecracker of a song 🧨, presenting ‘Bijuria’ from ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’! Featuring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Rohit Saraf and Sanya Malhotra in the video, the song is composed by Tanishk Bagchi and Ravi Pawar. Sung by Sonu Nigam and Asees Kaur and penned by Sonu Nigam and Tanishk Bagchi, hit play, turn it up, and let the beat take over! 🔥🎧

#Bijuria #SunnySanskariKiTulsiKumari #VarunDhawan #JanhviKapoor #SonuNigam #TanishkBagchi 

Original music composer: Ravi Pawar 
New version reimagined by : Tanishk Bagchi
Singer: Sonu Nigam
Singer: Asees Kaur
Music Producer: Tanishk Bagchi
Original Lyrics by: Sonu Nigam & Ajay Jhingran
New Version Additional Lyrics by: Tanishk Bagchi
Tabla & Dholak: Raju Sardar, Sanjiv Sen, Sharafat, Arou
Female Chorus: Shudhi Ramani, Abhiruchi Singh, Megha Bhardwaj, Nikitha Venkatesh
Male Chorus: Vivek Naik, Rahul Chitnis, Sagar Lele, Santosh Bote
Chorus Recorded at: Input One
Recording Engineer: Sameer Dharap (Input One)
Chorus Recorded at: Studio 504
Recording Engineer: Rahul M Sharma (Studio 504)
Mix and Master Engineer: Eric Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Assistant Mix Engineer: Michael Edwin Pillai @ Future Sounds of Bombay
Special Thanks : Hero
Special Thanks: Sumeet Kr Tyagi
Music Supervisor: Azeem Dayani
Sr Associate Music Supervisor: Tanvi Asher
Jr Associate Music Supervisor: Vasundhara Misra
Music Team: Heer Kamdar

Dharma Productions & Mentor Disciple Entertainment present 
A Dharma Productions Film
Starring Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor, Sanya Malhotra, & Rohit Saraf
Directed by Shashank Khaitan
Produced by Hiroo Yash Johar, Karan Johar, Adar Poonawalla, Apoorva Mehta & Shashank Khaitan
Co-produced by Marijke deSouza 
Written by Shashank Khaitan
Dialogues by Shashank Khaitan & Ishita Moitra

Director Of Choreography: Piyush - Shazia
Song Editor: Rishabh Shetty 
Asst Editor: Hrushi

Releasing on 2nd October, 2025

Lyrics:

Bann jaye-gi, yeh bann jaye-gi, re teri dhulania (x2)

Tujhe lage na najariya,
Kyun na odhe tu chunariya
Oh tujhe lage na najariya, odh le chunariya

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
Giraye re bijuria, bijuria

Bijuriaaaaa

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
Giraye re bijuria, bijuria

(Music)
Haye tera sharmana, tauba tera itraana
Jo bhi dekhe ho jaye woh deewana tera

Sone jaisa tan tera, uff bhola pan tera
Mujko bhi kar gaya deewana tera

O sun baki re gujariya,
Yahi bole hai dagaria
Sun baki re gujariya, bole ye dagaria

Lachke kamariya toh chhalke
Gagariya ki luti re bajaria (x2)

(Music)

Ooo…lachke kamariya toh thirke bijuria
Bachke dagariya toh girke bijuria

Oore bijuria x 2

Naino se maare chori aisan bijuria…aaahhh

Oh mujhe lage na najariya,
Maine odhe li chunariya
mujhe lage na najariya,
odhe li chunariya,
Mera hi deewana mere
dil pe fida hai…
Banungi mein dhulaniya

Dhulaniaaaaa

Mera hi deewana mere
dil pe fida hai…
Banungi mein dhulaniya

Thirchhi nigahe mere dil pe
giraye re bijuria, bijuria (x2)

(Music)

Lachke kamariya toh
Bachke dagariya toh

Ohh ohh re bijuria
Naino se maare chori aisan bijuria…

Aaahhh…aaah…aaaaa!!

snippet.title: #Video | Kamariya Mein Peer | Khesari Lal New Song | Neelam Giri | New Bhojpuri Song | Bhojpuri Gana
snippet.description:
“कमरिया में पीर” – खेसारी लाल यादव और नीलम गिरी का नया धमाकेदार भोजपुरी गाना, अब आपके लिए हाज़िर है। इसमें है जबरदस्त म्यूज़िक, मस्त अंदाज़ और भोजपुरिया तड़का, जो बना देगा आपको झूमने पर मजबूर!

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song – Kamariya Mein Peer
Hindi - कमरिया में पीर
Singer – Khesari Lal Yadav & Shilpi Raj
Featuring – Neelam Giri
Lyrics - Nirjala NK
Music – Madhukar Anand

Video Credits:-

Director - Sumit Kumar & Rohit Shetty
Choreographer - Rohit Shetty 
DOP - Jason Nambardar
Editor : Nitin FCP 
Associate Editor : Narendra Jaiswal
Di studio -ARTS FOR PRODUCTION 
Colorist- Kunal Singh
Video by - Sushil Pandey (ZQE Pictures)
Production House: Siddhivinayak Media

Lyrics:-

M
नकीया चढ़वले बाड़ू
मुहवां फुलवले बाड़ू
काहे बिछवना गोरी
अलगे बिछवले बाड़ू
तऽ काहे खिसियालू धनी
कोरवा में आजा 
दऽ ना तनी माजा
F
राते बदन दिहलऽ तोड़ ए राजा
झकझोर ए राजा
कमरीये में पीर बाड़ा जोर ए राजा
============================
M
बोलऽ धनी डाक्टर या बैधा बोलाई
खईबू दवाई कि सूई लगवाई
F
दिनवा में फल फूल विटामीन खियावेलऽ
रात में एनर्जी तू खरचा करावेलऽ
M
हऽ तऽ मजबूरी बुझऽ हई तोहर राजा
सहऽ तनी साजा 
F
बथऽता देह पोरे पोर ए राजा
कमजोर ए राजा
कमरीये में पीर बाड़ा जोर ए राजा
============================
M
बनल मिजाज प्यार उमड़ल बेजोड़ हो 
मन करे रख दी पलंगिया के तोड़ हो
F
खुदही वकील खुदे बनऽ तारऽ जज हो
कहे निर्जलवा बनऽ तारऽ निरलज हो
M
प्यार करे दऽ ना बंद कऽ के दरवाजा
फील करबू ताजा
F
काटी लाल कईलऽ गाल गोर ए राजा
खखोर ए राजा
कमरीये में पीर बाड़ा जोर ए राजा
============================

#khesari 
#khesarilalyadav 
#saregamahumbhojpuri 
#neelamgiri 
#shilpiraj 
#bhojpurisong 
#bhojpurimusic

snippet.title: Night Changes - One Direction (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿Listen:  Night Changes - One Direction (Lyrics)

🏴󠁧󠁢󠁥󠁮󠁧󠁿Lyrics:

[Verse 1: Zayn & Liam]
Goin' out tonight, changes into somethin' red
Her mother doesn't like that kind of dress
Everything she never had, she's showin' off
Drivin' too fast, moon is breakin' through her hair
She's headin' for somethin' that she won't forget
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

[Chorus: All & Harry]
(Ooh) We're only gettin' older, baby
(Ooh) And I've been thinkin' about it lately
(Ooh) Does it ever drive you crazy
(Ah-ah-ah) Just how fast the night changes?
(Ooh) Everything that you've ever dreamed of
(Ooh) Disappearin' when you wake up
(Ooh) But there's nothin' to be afraid of
(Ah-ah-ah) Even when the night changes
(Ooh) It will never change me and you

[Verse 2: Louis & Niall]
Chasin' her tonight, doubts are runnin' round her head
He's waitin', hides behind a cigarette
Heart is beatin' loud and she doesn't want it to stop
Movin' too fast, moon is lightin' up her skin
She's fallin', doesn't even know it yet
Havin' no regrets is all that she really wants

snippet.title: Bipul Chettri - Eh Saathi (Official Music Video)
snippet.description:
'Eh Saathi' is the first release from the forthcoming album, 'Pravah'. As the title suggests, it's an ode to childhood friendships that transcends time. Almost written like a conversation piece put to music, the song embodies the notion of friendship that is something to nurture and celebrate, that you never take them for granted and its enduring nature of emphasizing loyalty, love, and the shared journey of life.

Please switch on the CC button for English subtitles.

MUSIC
Bipul Chettri - Vocals, Guitars, Backing Vocals 
Pranai Gurung - Guitars
Rahul Rai - Bass
Rythem Bansal - Keys/Organ
Shantanu Sudarshan - Drums/Percussions 
Sumimardor Diengdoh, Bhushan Man Amatya, Prashansa Pandey Amatya - Backing Vocals 

Written and arranged by Bipul Chettri.
Recorded at Baa Baa Black Sheep Studios, Plug ‘N’ Play Studios & Project Studio Productions.
Recording Engineers - Jonty Indra, Anindo Bose, Binaya Man Amatya 
Mixed & Mastered by Binaya Man Amatya
Album Cover Design - Manohar Rai
Album Cover Photography - Praveen Chettri
Producer - Bipul Chettri
Executive Producer - Sonam Tashi 

VIDEO
Directed by Dishant Pradhan
Director of Photography: Vashistha Pradhan 
Chief Assistant Director: Sujan Lamjel
Edited by: Dishant & Vazzu
Art Director: Tejistha Pradhan
Costume Designer: Pfulmaya
Assistant Costume Designer: Subeksha Gurung 
Assistant Cinematographer: Akash Pradhan 
Production House: Lasta Studio 
Assistant Production Manager: Nuhang Subba 
Colorist: Shiny Syko
Lead Cast: Rahul N Mukhia, Kewal Subba, Tenzein Choden, Yowash Lepcha, Adarsh Dewan, Kavya Pradhan.

LYRICS
ए साथी, कस्तो चल्दै छ तेरो जीवन?
मेरो नि ठीकै छ भन्नु, पर्यो यहाँ।
ए साथी, किन लाग्छ सबै नौलो यहाँ?
हामी यस्तै थियौं हैन, एक जमाना।

हुरी बतास संगै उड्ने गर्थ्यौं हामी,
रातभरी जागी, गाउने गर्थ्यौं हामी।
हार केहि संग मान्दैन थियौं हामी,
संसारलाई जिति सके थियौं हामी।
हैन साथी… आः हा…

ए साथी, थाहा छ हामी साना खिरी
तेरो बाको चुरोट चोरी, तान्ने गर्थ्यौं।
एक अर्काको लागि हामी कोही संग, 
लड्नु, मर्नु, जहिले नि रेडी हुन्थ्यौं।

दिनभरीभरी संगै बिताएनि,
रात परेपछि, फेरि भेट्ने गर्थ्यौं।
किन हो किन त्यो पलहरू सोची अझै,
हाँसी पठाउँद छु, सम्झी कुरा धेरै।
ए साथी… आः हा… आः हा…

मलाई चिन्ने अरू कोही
तं जति छैन जस्तो लाग्छ
मेरो कुरा तैंले नै बुझे जस्तो लाग्छ।

कति माया पाएँ, कति धोका खाएँ,
कति छाडि गए, कति टाढा आए।
तर त्यो जिन्दगी फेरि पाउन
म जेनै दिने छु साथि 
म जेनै गरने छु

ए साथी… ए साथी…
ए साथी… ए साथी…

© All Rights Reserved by BIPUL CHETTRI. 2025.

LYRICS
ए साथी, कस्तो चल्दै छ तेरो जीवन?
मेरो नि ठीकै छ भन्नु, पर्यो यहाँ।
ए साथी, किन लाग्छ सबै नौलो यहाँ?
हामी यस्तै थियौं हैन, एक जमाना।

हुरी बतास संगै उड्ने गर्थ्यौं हामी,
रातभरी जागी, गाउने गर्थ्यौं हामी।
हार केहि संग मान्दैन थियौं हामी,
संसारलाई जिति सके थियौं हामी।
हैन साथी… आः हा…

ए साथी, थाहा छ हामी साना खिरी
तेरो बाको चुरोट चोरी, तान्ने गर्थ्यौं।
एक अर्काको लागि हामी कोही संग, 
लड्नु, मर्नु, जहिले नि रेडी हुन्थ्यौं।

दिनभरीभरी संगै बिताएनि,
रात परेपछि, फेरि भेट्ने गर्थ्यौं।
किन हो किन त्यो पलहरू सोची अझै,
हाँसी पठाउँद छु, सम्झी कुरा धेरै।
ए साथी… आः हा… आः हा…

मलाई चिन्ने अरू कोही
तं जति छैन जस्तो लाग्छ
मेरो कुरा तैंले नै बुझे जस्तो लाग्छ।

कति माया पाएँ, कति धोका खाएँ,
कति छाडि गए, कति टाढा आए।
तर त्यो जिन्दगी फेरि पाउन
म जेनै दिने छु साथि 
म जेनै गरने छु

ए साथी… ए साथी…
ए साथी… ए साथी…

en.title: Bipul Chettri - Eh Saathi (Official Music Video)
en.description:
'Eh Saathi' is the first release from the forthcoming album, 'Pravah'. As the title suggests, it's an ode to childhood friendships that transcends time. Almost written like a conversation piece put to music, the song embodies the notion of friendship that is something to nurture and celebrate, that you never take them for granted and its enduring nature of emphasizing loyalty, love, and the shared journey of life.

Please switch on the CC button for English subtitles.

snippet.description:
❗कृपया ध्यान दें:❗
इस गाने के सभी कॉपीराइट Trimurti Music World के पास सुरक्षित हैं। कोई भी व्यक्ति या चैनल इस गाने को बिना अनुमति के अपने प्लेटफॉर्म पर री-अपलोड न करे।
🚫 ऐसा करने पर आपके चैनल पर Copyright Strike की कार्रवाई की जाएगी।
🙏 कृपया हमारी मेहनत का सम्मान करें।

"Marne Ke Baad Pyar Hua" एक दिल को छू जाने वाला Bhojpuri Sad Song है, जिसे अपनी soulful आवाज़ में गाया है Chand Jee ने। इस इमोशनल लव स्टोरी में Mani Meraj और Vannu D Great ने फीचरिंग में शानदार अभिनय किया है, वहीं Shahbaz Khan ने विलेन का दमदार किरदार निभाया है।

snippet.description:
LISA’s debut album, ‘Alter Ego’ is out now. Listen here: https://lisa.lnk.to/AlterEgo   
Shop vinyl, CDs, photobooks and more: https://lnk.to/LisaStore 

Follow LISA:

https://www.tiktok.com/@wearelloud
http://www.facebook.com/wearelloud
https://www.youtube.com/@wearelloud/videos

Lyrics:
I’ve been thinking 
That I got no idea what you’re thinking 
Are you happy? Are you sad?
Are you always gonna hate me for that night in Tokyo? 
When it ended 
I kinda hoped that it’d be open ended
But you never looked back 
Well I guess you can’t hold on to something once you let it go 
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I guess that I’m taking what I can get 
‘Cause I don’t get nothing new from your friends 
If you got the harder side of the break 
Then why is it harder for me to take 
There’s so much I might never get to say, ay
But I know a place 
Where we can be us
I know it ain’t real 
But it’s real enough 
From sun going down to sun coming up 
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is all that we’ll ever be
It’s bittersweet
At least a girl can dream 
I-I-I know it’s only in my mind
Playing three nights on the stereo
Like a movie scene, DiCaprio 
Oh l-I-I put my make up on just to fall asleep
It’s like you’re here with me 
Whenever I close my eyes
It’s taking me back in time
Been drowning in dreams lately 
Like it’s 2019 baby 
Whenever I’m missing you 
Call you up but I can’t get through
Don’t know where you sleep lately 
But I’ll see you in my dreams maybe 
We can catch up, drive down our old street
If all that we were is something we’ll never be
It’s bittersweet
Can we be friends at least

snippet.title: Anuv Jain X Lost Stories - Arz Kiya Hai (Official Video) | Coke Studio Bharat
snippet.description:
For centuries, poets have given voice to the human heart, shaping the language of love. #ArzKiyaHai carries that legacy forward as an intimate tribute rooted in India’s poetic tradition, embracing the unguarded honesty of speaking your heart. At its helm is India’s most popular independent artist, Anuv Jain, pairing delicate guitar work with achingly tender vocals that distill this very emotion into melody. Joining him is Indian electronic duo Lost Stories working their magic on the production of the track as well as performing on the harmonium.

Listen to Arz Kiya Hai: https://UMGI.lnk.to/ArzKiyaHai_CSBS3


*CREDITS*


Written, Composed, and Performed By: Anuv Jain

Producer: Lost Stories 

Additional Production and Additional Vocals: Sarthak Kalyani

Backing Vocals: Solomon Konwar Rengma, Anahita Singh

Acoustic Guitars, Electric Guitars, Charango, Bass Guitars: Keba Jeremiah

snippet.title: TROPHIES ARE GONE?!
snippet.description:
Learn everything about the biggest matchmaking change in Clash of Clans history and what it means for you.
This change is coming with our next big update, but we wanted to give you a heads up so you can prepare.
For the first time ever, you will be able to choose how you want to Clash. Whether you're looking for competitive battles or a more relaxed way to play, this change gives you the freedom to pick the experience that fits your goals.

Follow us on our Socials!
Twitter ► https://twitter.com/ClashofClans/
Instagram ► https://www.instagram.com/clashofclans 
Facebook ► https://www.facebook.com/ClashofClans 
TikTok ► https://www.tiktok.com/@clashofclans

Attack. Defend. Strategize. Download for free for mobile devices. supr.cl/PlayClashOfClans

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

Chief, are you having problems? Visit https://help.supercellsupport.com/clash-of-clans/en/

Privacy Policy:
https://supercell.com/en/privacy-policy/

Terms of Service:
https://supercell.com/en/terms-of-service/

https://supercell.com/en/parents/

snippet.title: Lukas Graham - 7 Years (Lyrics)
snippet.description:
Subscribe and press (🔔) to join the Notification Squad and stay updated with new uploads

Download Stream - http://smarturl.it/LukasGrahamAlbum

Follow Lukas Graham:
https://www.instagram.com/lukasgraham
https://www.facebook.com/LukasGraham
https://www.tiktok.com/@lukasgraham

Follow Gseven Records:
Instagram : https://www.instagram.com/gsevenrecords/
Facebook : https://www.facebook.com/gsevenrecords/

We have an official permission from the right holders to upload this music

Lyrics:

[Chorus]
Once, I was seven years old, my mama told me
Go make yourself some friends, or you'll be lonely
Once, I was seven years old

[Verse 1]
It was a big, big world, but we thought we were bigger
Pushing each other to the limits, we were learning quicker
By eleven, smoking herb and drinking burning liquor
Never rich, so we were out to make that steady figure

[Chorus]
Once, I was eleven years old, my daddy told me
Go get yourself a wife, or you'll be lonely
Once, I was eleven years old

[Verse 2]
I always had that dream like my daddy before me
So I started writing songs, I started writing stories
Something about that glory just always seemed to bore me
'Cause only those I really love will ever really know me

[Chorus]
Once, I was twenty years old, my story got told
Before the morning sun, when life was lonely
Once, I was twenty years old (Lukas Graham!)

[Verse 3]
I only see my goals, I don't believe in failure
'Cause I know the smallest voices, they can make it major
I got my boys with me, at least those in favor
And if we don't meet before I leave, I hope I'll see you later

[Chorus]
Once, I was twenty years old, my story got told
I was writing 'bout everything I saw before me
Once, I was twenty years old

[Bridge]
Soon, we'll be thirty years old, our songs have been sold
We've traveled around the world and we're still roaming
Soon, we'll be thirty years old

[Verse 4]
I'm still learning about life, 
my woman brought children for me
So I can sing them all my songs, and I can tell them stories
Most of my boys are with me, some are still out seeking glory
And some I had to leave behind, 
my brother, I'm still sorry

[Chorus]
Soon, I'll be sixty years old, my daddy got sixty-one
Remember life and then your life becomes a better one
I made a man so happy when I wrote a letter once
I hope my children come and visit once or twice a month
[Breakdown]
Soon, I'll be sixty years old, will I think the world is cold?
Or will I have a lot of children who can warm me?
Soon, I'll be sixty years old
Soon, I'll be sixty years old, will I think the world is cold?
Or will I have a lot of children who can hold me?
Soon, I'll be sixty years old

[Chorus]
Once, I was seven years old, my mama told me
"Go make yourself some friends, or you'll be lonely"
Once I was seven years old
Once I was seven years old

snippet.title: Ujan Shakya - Kumari (Official Lyrical Video)
snippet.description:
✨ Beauty isn’t just in how someone looks, it’s in the kindness they carry, the confidence in their steps, and the glow of their spirit. She has a charm that feels timeless — graceful, radiant, and powerful, almost like the living Goddess Kumari herself. Not in a religious sense, but in the way her presence inspires awe and respect. 🌸

On this vibrant occasion of Indrajatra, may we all celebrate not just traditions, but also the beauty of inner strength, purity, and joy. Here’s to good vibes, laughter, and the festival spirit all around! 🎉
